    <div class="moz-cite-prefix">I've been working on adding msvc/cmake
      support last year (pushed some msvc-related fixes that are at
      least in v1.7 and later) but I stopped at some point because there
      was not much interest for it, and because it's not easy to do some
      automatic testing.<br>
      <br>
      I am not sure what you mean with windows 6.x and x64, but last
      time I checked things seemed to work fine on Windows 7 64bits at
      least. What symbols are we using that are not not available
      anymore? When did they disappear?<br>
      <br>
      Brice<br>
